import {useState} from 'react'

function Signup(){
return(
    <form>
        <label htmlFor='E-mail'>
            Enter your e-mail:
        </label>
        <input type="email" required></input>
        <label htmlFor='E-mail'>
            Enter your username:
        </label>
    </form>
)
}

export default Signup
